div class="order-3 flex grow flex-wrap md:hidden md:grow-0"><div class="mt-4 w-full"> <button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-brand-green-700 hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm h-11">立即购买</button></div><div class="mx-2 mt-4 w-full"><div class=" font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊</span>29.99 美元</span><img class="mt-0 h-[15px]" src="/images/amazon-prime.svg" title="亚马逊 Prime" alt="Amazon Prime"></div></div></div></div></div></div><h2 id="light-awkward-places">灯光尴尬的地方</h2><p>在某些情况下，向黑暗区域供电带来的麻烦大于其价值。车库、地下室和壁橱都可能是您可能希望有一点额外的灯光的地方，但没有电线来添加任何灯光，而<a href="https://zdcs.link/Qx7EEP?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=rechargeable%20bulb&amp;short_url=Qx7EEP&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>可充电灯泡</u></a>或<a href="https://zdcs.link/QGVOOV?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=fixture&amp;short_url=QGVOOV&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>固定装置</u></a>可能是一种廉价的解决方案。选择充电灯的位置时，请记住，它需要定期放下来充电，因此将它们挂在可触及的地方是一个不错的选择。</p> ]]>;</content:encoded><link/> https://lifehacker.com/home/clever-uses-rechargeable-bulbs<dc:creator>贝卡·刘易斯</dc:creator><category><![CDATA[Home & Garden]]></category></item></channel></rss>